{"tid":494682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【童心未泯】可 愛 女 童 悉 心 打 扮 赴 盆 菜 宴 慰 勞 叔 伯 兄 弟","createTime":"2017-12-10T02:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T00:43:37.000Z","uid":24160,"like":31,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b6db3f4f245158602c943844a442ee4dbd49a471","tid":494682,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">印有七色彩虹的長袖外衣<br />\n配襯下身七色傘裙<br />\n顯得汪明荃女士活潑可愛動人<br />\n另外，紅色小斜揹袋更為汪氏增添多一份清純感<br />\n難怪兩位高層再親近阿姐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6776b853gy1fm95f36ks1j20qo0zkah9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F6776b853gy1fm95f36ks1j20qo0zkah9.jpg&h=e2b282c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對比上次坦露事業線的汪氏，陳博士唔知有冇再度大膽公開表白呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/10/095003_a34d550796493090d5cfb12eaca8c0a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F095003_a34d550796493090d5cfb12eaca8c0a4.jpg&h=84b2315f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(連Do 姐都不屑陳博士咁明目張膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">溫故知新</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg&h=ee59598d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪明荃博士身穿紅連身裙滿臉春光的回答高層首長問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6776b853gy1fm95f4qzxaj20qo0zkwmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F6776b853gy1fm95f4qzxaj20qo0zkwmz.jpg&h=d121b40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂氏與汪氏歡欣嘅合照<br />\n此動人時光令人遙想起另一張溫馨義工長者合照<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/20170319/5QNs-fycnyhk9480544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F20170319%2F5QNs-fycnyhk9480544.jpg&h=ce20ae37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/64QQBns.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F64QQBns.gif&h=55dee924&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/64QQBns.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F64QQBns.gif&h=55dee924&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/64QQBns.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F64QQBns.gif&h=55dee924&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/64QQBns.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F64QQBns.gif&h=55dee924&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/64QQBns.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F64QQBns.gif&h=55dee924&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/64QQBns.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F64QQBns.gif&h=55dee924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"8223b389684e2c7b8e4ba186b0e764114accf440","tid":494682,"uid":24160,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dsfgXjx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdsfgXjx.jpg&h=aaf3f200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896165f55d1b20b099453f8412d757269998093d","tid":494682,"uid":24160,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:07:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">​<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/3d797d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F3d797d.gif&h=eda1a8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/3d797d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F3d797d.gif&h=eda1a8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/3d797d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F3d797d.gif&h=eda1a8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汪明荃 - 傾城之戀 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=udfNVz1sHsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DudfNVz1sHsU&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO20%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bf9a9bd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=udfNVz1sHsU</a><br />\n<br />\n王祖藍 - 熱咖啡<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YEwmqEhGBwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYEwmqEhGBwg&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO20%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=560b6302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YEwmqEhGBwg</a><br />\n<br />\n容祖兒 - 京華春夢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dq6nAMAxu9k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDq6nAMAxu9k&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO20%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=12d046be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dq6nAMAxu9k</a><br />\n<br />\n汪明荃 - 銀河<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJVarFAUogs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmJVarFAUogs&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO20%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7d40cc07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJVarFAUogs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/c3f3c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fc3f3c2.jpg&h=d7ffd50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪明荃博士身穿黑色&quot;中門大開&quot;晚裝乘坐駕進入半島酒店會場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/4fc9dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F4fc9dc.jpg&h=9c466b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪博士更與一眾司儀合照，眾人服飾顯得汪氏晚裝簡約而高貴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/840504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F840504.jpg&h=5d81a743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏與王浩信合照<br />\n此照更能清楚觀察到汪氏事業線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/de13f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fde13f4.jpg&h=a4b7a8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/6006d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F6006d2.jpg&h=a6873272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n王浩信難抵阿姐魅力<br />\n害羞得不敢側目凝視<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/d37ace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fd37ace.jpg&h=f1be7d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏換上另一套米色晚裝，盡顯其玲瓏身段<br />\n企喺上等人及一眾甘草演員旁<br />\n更後生成廿年有多，唔似七十歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/d296c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fd296c1.jpg&h=b2c97a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n及後，汪氏再換上閃爆護肩低胸晚裝保護其隨歲月而退化嘅肩膀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其閃爍裝飾簡直閃爆所有重量級嘉賓, 包括胡定欣, Miss Chan Chan, 容祖祖等人<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/209fe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F209fe4.jpg&h=7573fded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/6b0d50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F6b0d50.jpg&h=ec2af2dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/4_img/upload/d411fbc6/20171111/l0eo-fynstfh4874445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2F4_img%2Fupload%2Fd411fbc6%2F20171111%2Fl0eo-fynstfh4874445.jpg&h=ce69249e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏亦曾身穿紅色高叉晚裝進出會場<br />\n右邊男子為曾向汪氏問價之高層<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg&h=f064a680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿姐真係忙一日換幾套衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 七十明荃 風韻猶存<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊重溫阿姐演唱會之風采 [5分鐘精華]<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/INS26vhNJdQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=